channel.title: [rs2] RuneScape Helping buddy - simple and easy to use tool - 0wnag3 -
channel.description:
hey,
My *runescape helping buddy* is probly the most basic script you will find, it works around you the user pressing the buttons according to a command you would like to complete for example:
[center]. Built in autominer/colorless setup just chose the rock you wish to mine! . Auto Spammer with the ability to chose your color or . text effect/this includes all effects . ScreenShot taker, take as many screenshots as you . like, they are automaticly saved at a hit of a botton . AutoLogin on demand . AutoDropper at the hit of a key . Includes my updated antiban options![/center]
once you run the script you will find out how to use these, they all revolve around the "f" key's
